  "texts": [
    "More advanced texture features proposed for plankton recognition include Local Binary Patterns (LBP) (Ojala et al. 2002; Schulze et al. 2013; Chang et al. 2016; Lisin 2006; Yu and Sun 2023), and Gabor descriptors (Idrissa and Acheroy 2002; Sánchez et al. 2019b; Bueno et al. 2017).",
    "The third widely utilized group of image features is local features that typically combine the feature detectors and descriptors.",
    "Feature detectors search the image for characteristic interest points or regions that contain useful information for the task, i.e.",
    "plankton recognition.",
    "Local feature descriptors then quantify these regions."
  ],
